Class CompleteFreeSpaceExpansionRoom

java.lang.Object
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.autoroute.FreeSpaceExpansionRoom
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.autoroute.CompleteFreeSpaceExpansionRoom
All Implemented Interfaces:
CompleteExpansionRoom, ExpansionRoom, SearchTreeObject, ShapeTree.Storable, Comparable<Object>
public class CompleteFreeSpaceExpansionRoom extends FreeSpaceExpansionRoom implements CompleteExpansionRoom, SearchTreeObject
An expansion room, whose shape is completely calculated, so that it can be stored in a shape tree.
